name: FindMyRep
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: find my rep
des:
You can use this skill to lookup the details of government officials so that you may contact them via phone or email. You can ask for all of your reps information, or ask by a specific position such as "Mayor", "Governor", "Senator", etc.

We hope you'll use this skill to help make a difference in your community by reaching out to your local, state, and federal governments to make sure they support your beliefs.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
